that he was totally obsessed with you.

616
00:43:47.916 --> 00:43:48.751
He was?

617
00:43:48.834 --> 00:43:51.503
Yeah, come on. Wait, you didn't notice?

618
00:43:52.129 --> 00:43:54.590
No, actually. No.

619
00:43:54.673 --> 00:43:55.841
That's right.

620
00:43:55.924 --> 00:43:58.093
