632
00:44:35.673 --> 00:44:38.634
And he was super controlling
and just crazy jealous.

633
00:44:42.137 --> 00:44:44.890
Wish... I wish I could hear
her side of the story.

634
00:44:46.100 --> 00:44:47.309
