if you got that man alone.

763
00:58:07.233 --> 00:58:10.361
Hey, man.
Sorry to hear about your wife, too.

764
00:58:10.445 --> 00:58:12.280
Ex. Ex-wife.

765
00:58:12.906 --> 00:58:14.115
Yeah, well, either way.

766
00:58:17.410 --> 00:58:18.703
